OL,3,CCritical Care Unit for 'sickest
OL,4,Cpatients' delayed as work overruns
OL,6,FThe opening of a new Critical Care
OL,7,FUnit at Guernsey's Princess Elizabeth
OL,8,FHospital has been delayed due to
OL,9,Fconstruction work overrunning.
OL,11,FThe department will look after the
OL,12,F"sickest patients" and offer extra
OL,13,Fsurgical capacity to meet ongoing
OL,14,Fdemand but officials say extra time is
OL,15,Fneeded to make sure it is fit for
OL,16,Fpurpose.
