OL,3,CCritical Care Unit for 'sickest
OL,4,Cpatients' delayed as work overruns
OL,6,FThe first phase of the Hospital
OL,7,FModernisation Programme was set to be
OL,8,Fcompleted by the end of autumn 2024,
OL,9,Fwith a new finish date listed as the
OL,10,Fbeginning of 2025.
OL,12,FGuernsey's Health President, Deputy Al
OL,13,FBrouard, explains that the facility's
OL,14,Fcomplex make-up has caused the delay
OL,15,Fbut adds that structural work is
OL,16,Fcomplete and the project still falls
OL,17,Fwithin budget.
