OL,3,CCritical Care Unit for 'sickest
OL,4,Cpatients' delayed as work overruns
OL,6,FHe says: "All the timelines are our
OL,7,Fown self-imposed timelines, so there's
OL,8,Fno critical need that we have to be
OL,9,Fdone at a certain date.
OL,11,F"We'd like to make sure that we do it
OL,12,Fin a controlled way and we don't rush
OL,13,Fthe last bit.
OL,15,F"There's a few bits of snagging that
OL,16,Fneeds to happen and we'd rather do
OL,17,Fthat properly, one time only, rather
OL,18,Fthan trying to enter the building too
OL,19,Fsoon."
