OL,3,CCritical Care Unit for 'sickest
OL,4,Cpatients' delayed as work overruns
OL,6,FThe Critical Care Unit will open with
OL,7,Feight beds and have the capacity to
OL,8,Fincrease to 12, depending on how many
OL,9,Fpatients are cared for over the next
OL,10,Fdecade.
OL,12,FPhase One will also see a new Post
OL,13,FAnaesthetic Care Unit created with 10
OL,14,Fbeds.
OL,16,FLead nurse John Eaton says the project
OL,17,Fis "really exciting" but adds that
OL,18,Fthey have to ensure it is appropriate
OL,19,Ffor patients before they move in.
