OL,3,CCritical Care Unit for 'sickest
OL,4,Cpatients' delayed as work overruns
OL,6,FHe explains: "While the building looks
OL,7,Fnearly finished, we've got lots of
OL,8,Fmedical equipment to install and lots
OL,9,Fof clinical testing to do.
OL,11,F"The sickest and most vulnerable
OL,12,Fpatients in the hospital will be cared
OL,13,Ffor here so we've got to make sure
OL,14,Fit's fully equipped and absolutely
OL,15,Fsafe before we move them."
